com.hjortsholm.contacts.database

Annotation Type TableField


  • @Repeatable(value=TableFields.class)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface TableField

    Table Field

    A annotation tag for defining table fields for a class used to automate table creation, verification and insertion of objects with this annotation.
    Since:
    10/04/2018
    Version:
